cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual tracking and proposes a method to improve the robustness of correlation filter learning. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes three sparsity related loss functions to improve the overall tracking performance. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a more robust tracking model. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with real-time visual tracking. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in various challenging situations, which is relevant to robotics applications.
